casebody.data:
Anthony ROGERS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1957 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. October 3, 2018 EMAS, LUCK and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of habeas corpus alleging ineffective assistance of appellate counsel, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
